<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>PetsMania - Ultimate Mart For Pets</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/style.css">
<link rel="shortcut icon" href="../assets/Favicon.ico" type="image/jpeg">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/auth.css">
</head>
<body>
<header class="header">
  <a href="/index" class="logo"><i class="fa-solid fa-paw"></i>Pet<span>Care</span></a>
  <nav class="navbar">
    <a href="/index">Home</a>
    <a href="/services">Services</a>
    <a href="/pricing">Pricing</a>
    <a href="/about">About Us</a>
    <a href="/contact">Contact Us</a>
    <a href="/auth/login">Login</a>
  </nav>
  <i id="menu-btn" class="fas fa-bars"></i>
</header>
<div style="
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
  min-height: 80vh;
  background: none;
">
  <form action="/auth/login" method="POST" style="
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: .5rem;
    box-shadow: .5rem .5rem 0 rgba(22, 160, 133, .2);
    border: .2rem solid rgba(0,0,0,1);
    padding: 2.5rem 2rem 2rem 2rem;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 420px;
    margin: 2rem auto;
    text-align: center;
    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
  ">
    <h2 style="
      color: var(--orange);
      text-shadow: .4rem .4rem 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, .2);
      font-size: 2.2rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      letter-spacing: .1rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    ">Login</h2>
    <% if (typeof error !== 'undefined') { %>
      <div style="
        color: #fff;
        background: #e74c3c;
        padding: .7rem 1rem;
        border-radius: .5rem;
        font-weight: bold;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        text-align: center;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(200,0,0,0.08);
      "><%= error %></div>
    <% } %>
    <div style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem; text-align: left;">
      <label for="contact" style="
        color: var(--black);
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        margin-bottom: .5rem;
        display: block;
        font-weight: 500;
      ">Email:</label>
      <input type="text" name="contact" id="contact" required placeholder="Enter email" style="
        width: 100%;
        padding: 1rem;
        border-radius: .5rem;
        border: .2rem solid rgba(0,0,0,1);
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        color: var(--black);
        margin-top: .3rem;
        font-family: inherit;
      ">
    </div>
    <button type="submit" style="
      background: var(--orange);
      color: var(--white);
      border: none;
      border-radius: .5rem;
      padding: .9rem 2.5rem;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      box-shadow: .5rem .5rem 0 rgba(22, 160, 133, .2);
      cursor: pointer;
      margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
      transition: background 0.2s;
    "
    onmouseover="this.style.background='rgb(0, 128, 0)'"
    onmouseout="this.style.background='rgb(200, 132, 7)'"
    >Send Login Code</button>
    <div style="margin-top: 1.5rem; text-align: center; font-size: 1rem;">
      <a href="/auth/register" style="color: var(--orange); text-decoration: underline; margin: 0 .7rem;">Register</a>
      |
      <a href="/auth/reset-password" style="color: var(--green); text-decoration: underline; margin: 0 .7rem;">Forgot Password?</a>
    </div>
  </form>
</div>

<!-- footer starts -->
<section class="footer">
  <div class="footer-content">
     <h3><i class="fa-solid fa-paw"></i>Pet<span>Care</span></h3> 
     <p>PetCare is a pet caring shop, where we provide facilites and various useful treatments. We offer Massage, a good ground, expert staff, good facilites and much more! Visit us anytime :). We are closed only on thrusday and our regular timings are 9:00AM to 10:00PM.</p>
